<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS: EXECUTIVE JOINS ELSINORE AEROSPACE SERVICES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 David M. Lagger has joined Elsinore Aerospace Services in Newport Beach as 
vice president of business development.In his new position, he will coordinate 
the development of customer programs for Elsinore's Aircraft Systems 
Integration Group. Lagger was previously director of business development of 
Lockheed Commercial Aircraft Center in San Bernardino. Before that, he held 
management positions in planning and development, maintenance and production 
control for Tracor Aviation and People Express Airlines. 
</P>
