<TEXT>
<P>
 Colin Fort has been appointed vice president of First American Trust Co., a 
Santa Ana provider of personal, employee benefit and investment trust 
services.He is responsible for client service, account management and 
administration and new business for San Diego County. He also oversees all 
company personal trust services for the area. Before joining First American, 
