<P>
HOLIDAY CLOSINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Today is Memorial Day. The following schedule is in effect: 
</P>
<P>
 * City, county and federal offices are closed. 
</P>
<P>
 * County, state and federal courthouses are closed. 
</P>
<P>
 * City and county libraries are closed.  
</P>
<P>
 * Banks and savings and loans are closed. 
</P>
<P>
 * Schools, colleges and universities are closed. Los Alamitos Unified School 
District kindergarten through eighth grades will also be closed Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 * Mail: There is no postal service. 
</P>
<P>
 * Trash: Trash will be collected one day late throughout the week, except in 
Anaheim and Orange. Residents in these cities with regular pickup today should 
place their trash curbside on Tuesday.  
</P>
<P>
 * Buses: OCTA buses run on Sunday schedule.  
</P>
<P>
 * Parks: All city- and county-run parks are open during regular hours. 
</P>
